text: Curtain Call at Cactus Creek is a 1950 American western comedy movie directed by Charles Lamont and starring Donald O'Connor, Gale Storm, Walter Brennan, Vincent Price, Eve Arden, Joe Sawyer, Chick Chandler, Rex Lease. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1950 comedy movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Charles Lamont Category:Universal Pictures movies
